snippet.title: Gears POP! - E3 2018 - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Gears of War and Funko POP! join forces to bring a new Gears game to mobile devices for the first time. Coming in 2019.

Audio Description: https://youtu.be/G6OnnGxadDg
